.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7609ae8a0151ab12cdab49ad14fb6e8ffb789f","tid":123033,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"唔乘機討論埋roadshow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676cb1bd9f310e4304f692b5a5676e5b33b52c99","tid":123033,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:00:45.000Z","msg":"新車好多都冇裝ROADSHOW，係舊車先有"},{"pid":"5fff7dc2e72ca05e9fb407245aa41b9215203d04","tid":123033,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新車好多都冇裝ROADSHOW，係舊車先有</blockquote><br />\n一路裝緊"},{"pid":"72ac3501da5e1e0a1a50b2eff82292ce4c3fb495","tid":123033,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>D櫈可唔可以換撚曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚柒硬呀，同埋可唔可以唔好咁光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d車既光管係光到刺眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n城巴藍光都未出聲</blockquote><br />\n城巴最新用黃光，得兩三批車藍光<br />\n<br />\n九巴都有藍光燈，而最新既係用白燈，仲有翻新左既車都係白色LED(呢d最刺眼)"},{"pid":"60ba73184bdbd87abdfb6e6b0a4a176f35762ecb","tid":123033,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整返d可以打開嘅車窗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家根本係毒氣室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新座位好撚膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好窄</blockquote><br />\n鬧左好耐<br />\n個隻櫈平，加上要塞多d位，變左頂頭頂腳"},{"pid":"abd480c589f101c91adb3a6a24b411d508aec4ff","tid":123033,"uid":2